{"tid":1245864,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政總唔開 咪去探下老母囉","createTime":"2019-06-20T13:04:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T13:21:47.000Z","uid":28870,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f0be7e363f639c0bd59fc7c72f4459aed39ab8fc","tid":1245864,"uid":28870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T13:04:08.000Z","msg":"邊有人搵人唔去人地屋企咁蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fad491bb9228cb9dd88e06b6f6566f15c37126aa","tid":1245864,"uid":28870,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T13:04:48.000Z","msg":"[quote]【請為621廣泛報料，聽朝七點，政總集合】<br />\n【不內哄、不分化、各自上山】<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>======20/6/2019 15:00更新======</strong></span><br />\n立法會、政總、警總、禮賓府警察勢力分報圖，持續收料，一直更新。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5rtOBOy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5rtOBOy.jpg&h=eae4919c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n歡迎加入討論: <strong>圖解香港禮賓府旅遊路線</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1241712/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1241712/page/1</a><br />\n<strong>更多細節請用追故模式</strong><br />\n===============================<br />\n禮賓府高空、地則及2018香港地圖懶人包<br />\n===============================<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/34yGdCf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F34yGdCf.jpg&h=2aced7f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8gB8C11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8gB8C11.jpg&h=f5e08abb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C6aA1c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC6aA1c0.jpg&h=0cd9b552&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n禮賓府交通路線<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pZoOuRy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpZoOuRy.jpg&h=6ca9e50d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5v6z9Rz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5v6z9Rz.jpg&h=7291e991&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n====================<br />\n禮賓府建議地鐵步行路線<br />\n====================<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JUqEBwz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJUqEBwz.jpg&h=f978913f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n===============<br />\n禮賓府地下通道新聞<br />\n===============<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ceZBDKW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FceZBDKW.jpg&h=7ac3a5fb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n===============================<br />\n夢見好多人想開放日遊覽禮賓府。<br />\n但聽聞條斜路好危險，驚人多出現意外。<br />\n為安全著想，出席任何活動前，<span style=\"color: red;\">大家都有義務了解該地環境</span>，<br />\n希望各位唔好一知半解的情況下跟隨人流，造成危險。<br />\n<br />\n樓主現時收集以下的資料及圖片，作學術研究之用 :<br />\n1.急救站、飲水機、洗手間或可設立急救站空地等休息位置<br />\n2.立法會、政總、警總、禮賓府野生犬隻出沒或聚居地點 (可以Google map mark比我最好)<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[同我推晒佢] 力抗膠post 621行動討論整合</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1242813/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1242813/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後，立法會、政總、警總、禮賓府全部都相當有歷史價值，係一家大細親子好去處，大家記得要遵守秩序，<span style=\"color: red;\">去之前記得做足功課</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />平時無開放千奇唔好去呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3875c5e6d0191b5a8264b3323d1fffdfbca98b6","tid":1245864,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T13:05:27.000Z","msg":"最驚佢老母都唔係到 又空城"},{"pid":"2f307377dce3f8363915f6816c187b36426e1b11","tid":1245864,"uid":28870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T13:06:16.000Z","msg":"據講林奠聽日會出現係 九龍灣兒童醫院<br />\n但冇fact check冇source<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceed8c423eeba6539248446055f64fa99569e01b","tid":1245864,"uid":28870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T13:06:28.000Z","msg":"piah"},{"pid":"c11b24927e1f3e939ec661af4ffdd1e8dd01a61c","tid":1245864,"uid":4496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T13:06:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac87b11b27f1ab8b4714c1c11bc5920a4c1b2eba","tid":1245864,"uid":28870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T13:06:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"86261d70c097fc779edce3417bf071edec4a6639","tid":1245864,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T13:07:30.000Z","msg":"有秘道"},{"pid":"cbfa94f75edf8a3db2d7b4cc4827deaf26d638b8","tid":1245864,"uid":28870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T13:07:37.000Z","msg":"時間唔洗問喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都係七點<br />\n探老母邊有得講擇時辰<br />\n盡孝"},{"pid":"3fd0e9866a9d99659ddfb31d592879ff474f2884","tid":1245864,"uid":28870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86261d70c097fc779edce3417bf071edec4a6639","tid":1245864,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T13:07:30.000Z","msg":"有秘道"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T13:08:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n逼佢出黎對話姐<br />\n又唔係要對佢造成不利<br />\n佢要 鬼鼠 咪有得佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef09dc50a9cae4b41056fc98b9087e55bb8ede25","tid":1245864,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T13:09:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1348b3388b857d370137a4a55d2e6347a8540527","tid":1245864,"uid":264394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T13:21:47.000Z","msg":"推"}]}